{"id":252171,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/维权网-江西省新余市数百人举行反日示威游行（/","date":"2012-09-16T21:01:14Z","modified":"2012-10-16T08:23:31Z","title":"维权网 | 江西省新余市数百人举行反日示威游行（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div align=\"center\"><span>   </span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span>（维权网信息员顾中民报道）今天（</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">16</span><span>日）上午，江西省新余市数百人举行反日示威游行。约</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">8</span><span>点半钟，游行队伍在城南抱石公园东门广场聚集出发。其路线为：抱石公园→火车站→劳动路立交桥→赣新路口→仙来大道→城北广场→长青南路立交桥→抱石公园。</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"6852834633822489615\"></a>  </p>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>游行队伍一路上撑着国旗、打着标语、喊着口号：“日本滚出钓鱼岛，钓鱼岛是中国的！”“扬我中华，抵制日货！”“声援上海大游行，今日新余看行动！”“坚决打击日本军国主义狼子野心！”“驱逐倭寇，勿忘国耻！”等等，群情激奋，震撼人心。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>游行队伍主要由青年学生和自由职业者组成。前有警用摩托车开道，左右均有警察夹道护送，后有警用摩托和步行警察压阵。独立参选人刘萍和李思华说，最让他们吃惊的是，游行队伍中间杂着许多便衣警察，其中很多是他们认识的。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>刘萍说有一个穿黑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">T</span><span>恤衫、黑长裤、黑皮鞋，真正是上下一身黑的黑色便衣警察，就是“两会”期间将她从北京戴黑头套押回新余的国保人员之一。间杂在游行队伍中的便衣警察是维持秩序，还是参与游行？如果是参与游行，为何不穿着警察制服公开以警察身份游行？</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span>游行队伍回到出发地抱石公园后，游行负责人宣布解散前通知后天的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">9</span><span>·</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>再此举行更大规模的反日示威游行，集结地点和游行线路不变。刘萍和李思华说，希望下一次游行队伍中的便衣警察不会像今天这样给人留下太多的神秘、猜测和恐惧；更希望这种游行是单纯的爱国反日保钓示威游行，而不会变质变味，被别有用心者所利用。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TqcKpwUsvSY/UFXkjAY2aPI/AAAAAAAAOh8/jw4RaxBN3Ro/s1600/CIMG2520.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"300\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-TqcKpwUsvSY/UFXkjAY2aPI/AAAAAAAAOh8/jw4RaxBN3Ro/s400/CIMG2520.JPG\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-kCyA9EqkZRE/UFXkknMtowI/AAAAAAAAOiE/S-o9OHcXxAc/s1600/CIMG2550.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-kCyA9EqkZRE/UFXkknMtowI/AAAAAAAAOiE/S-o9OHcXxAc/s320/CIMG2550.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2KVvXBknNSE/UFXknAit_II/AAAAAAAAOiM/BvX3rXcHafY/s1600/CIMG2571.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-2KVvXBknNSE/UFXknAit_II/AAAAAAAAOiM/BvX3rXcHafY/s320/CIMG2571.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-D8IT_JkrCJQ/UFXkpM9MCMI/AAAAAAAAOiU/wcunuojAw_0/s1600/CIMG2764.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-D8IT_JkrCJQ/UFXkpM9MCMI/AAAAAAAAOiU/wcunuojAw_0/s320/CIMG2764.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FyaHTG3-mQI/UFXkrBjbqgI/AAAAAAAAOic/sgZPhGwqMFg/s1600/CIMG2824.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-FyaHTG3-mQI/UFXkrBjbqgI/AAAAAAAAOic/sgZPhGwqMFg/s320/CIMG2824.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Di9bi9NqhSM/UFXkuRVsIcI/AAAAAAAAOik/mojHYY9bk78/s1600/CIMG2525.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-Di9bi9NqhSM/UFXkuRVsIcI/AAAAAAAAOik/mojHYY9bk78/s320/CIMG2525.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div align=\"left\"><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n<div><img width=\"1\" height=\"1\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/tracker/751033951089627103-5219628441868490507?l=wqw2010.blogspot.com\" alt=\"\" /></div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in